    ?location rdfs:label ?locationName .
    ?location geo:hasGeometry/geo:asWKT ?mapGeometry .

    ?quest geo:hasGeometry/geo:asWKT ?questGeometry .
    
    FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?questGeometry, ?cityGeometry))
  }
}
GROUP BY ?location ?locationName
ORDER BY DESC(?questCount)
